meta {
  name: 06 - Week 2 Agent
  seq: 6
}

docs {
  The Week 2 multi-agent surface. Real file: `public/agent.php`. One
  CSRF-checked POST = one full supervisor run: the deterministic supervisor
  routes to the evidence-retriever worker (always, for a question) and the
  intake-extractor worker (when a `document` is attached), the LLM-backed
  composer drafts a claims answer over chart facts its tools fetched, and
  the critic (deterministic V1-V6 verifier) hard-gates the draft.

  Run "00 - Auth Bootstrap" first for `csrf_token`. The response's
  `correlation_id` links the whole handoff tree
  (`supervisor` -> `worker`(s) -> `verify`); request 2 opens the
  dashboard waterfall for it (admin ACL).
}
